Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0

Package: clouseau
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bpfcc-tools, procps
Description: Claude process monitor
 Continuously monitors Claude AI CLI processes using eBPF tracing.
 Tracks file access (opensnoop), network connections (tcpconnect),
 and subprocess execution (execsnoop). Logs each Claude session to
 a timestamped directory under LOG_DIR.
